      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration (62 mm vertebral body height, standard rod length per ASTM F1717). COU encompasses only this configuration; however, the factor is assessed below required level because no parametric variation of test conditions was performed to confirm model extrapolation fidelity. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given that the COU is explicitly bounded to the single F1717 configuration. Achieved level 2 is below required level 3; risk accepted by credibility assessment team given bounded COU scope.",
